      "title": "Ruling party parliamentary committee meeting today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The ruling party parliamentary committee meeting will be held today under the leadership of President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "The decision was taken after a discussion between the President and Speaker Sushil Premajayant.",
        "Accordingly, this meeting will be held today at 5 pm at the President's Secretariat. (a)"
